title: Racionalni Vyziva
description: Stocks gluten-free, vegetarian, vegan, and healthy food products. Has vegan cakes, buchteln, sandwiches, burgers, salty croissants, and pizza among other stuff (best days are Tue and Wed); oils, grains, plant milks, healthy sweets; a shelf of natural cosmetics. You can order a organic vegetables box with one week advance notice. Located in the northeast suburbs.
